<h3><a href="https://conf.tube/c/apconf_channel/videos" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">ActivityPub Conference</a></h3>
<p>A conference about the present and future of ActivityPub, the world’s leading federated social web standard. This two day event will include presentations of prepared talks on Saturday followed by a loosely structured unconference on Sunday.</p>
